Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:11.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(220,220)\fs28}大家都會倍顯積極哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:30.03,title ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(215,240)\fs38\bord0}待續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:40.03,title ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,180)\fs35}能力與力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:17.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:17.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:18.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰火？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:19.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:20.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是之前的那個事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是第五起了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟之前一樣爆炸本身的規模不大並沒有產生傷者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:02.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:07.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作為愉快犯來說還真讓人笑不出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:07.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs15}愉快犯:  製造騷亂以從中取樂的犯罪者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:09.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  關於嫌犯的線索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:13.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天  終於找到線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:16.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  您聽說過「虛空爆炸」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:16.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(393,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「虛空爆炸」…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:21.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指重力子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:22.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論哪起事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:28.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在爆炸之前通過衛星都觀測到了重力子的急促的加速運動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:32.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如將鋁罐作為基點將重力子以爆炸性的速度加速
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:35.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在瞬間往四周擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:39.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說把鋁罐變成了炸彈  這個就是原理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:42.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是鋁罐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:44.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:45.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道這是能力者的所作所為了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話只需查一下學院都市的「書庫」不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,328)\fs18}Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:56.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為所有學生的能力數據都記錄在案了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然已經搜查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所答覆的能力是「量子變速」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,328)\fs18}Synchrotron
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:06.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且能力還要足夠將鋁罐變為炸彈的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:08.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有一名大能力的學生能符合條件了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:08.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,328)\fs18}Level 4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那個人就是嫌犯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:13.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她有不在場證明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:16.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人一直住著院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:19.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能引起這一連串的事件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:20.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:22.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是又無解了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:27.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書庫的數據應該也不會有缺漏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:27.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,328)\fs18}Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:33.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是還有沒記錄在案的能力者什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:36.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我也去幫忙去找嫌犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:38.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是免了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:40.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:44.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才是不是想著「這個說不定會有趣呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:50.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「根據對手強弱我也能一試身手」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:51.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事怎麼可…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝傻也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子我早就看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我很早就跟你說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人怎麼說也是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:02.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持治安的活動就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:06.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我們風紀委員就行了  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:06.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:12.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為帶著不嚴肅的好奇心和興趣就能勝任風紀委員那就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:12.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:15.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了  我沒打算這樣做…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:19.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請你在此時此地發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:23.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一  不許隨隨便便地趟這起事件的混水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:25.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著  這算什麼啊  這種單方面的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:30.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二  即使萬一不幸被捲入事件當中  也嚴禁單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待風紀委員的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為  你們來之前事情都已經解決…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:37.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三  不許在裙子底下穿短褲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟這個無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:45.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籍此機會順便從服裝和其他種種生活態度上重新審視自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:51.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  姐姐大人非常缺乏作為常盤台的王牌的自覺這點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:52.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子也感到非常擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  請讓我說完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:58.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您有些許自覺的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:02.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會抱著玩具熊睡覺  往浴缸裏放橡皮鴨什麼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:05.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是該從這種小孩子的興趣當中畢業了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:06.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那彩色調的幼稚內衣和睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說也是學園都市第三的超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名聲在外的「超電磁炮」…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:13.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(298,326)}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:17.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我老媽嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說呢初春同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:25.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之能先坐下嗎  御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:38.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是推測  白井同學只是不想御阪學姐捲入危險當中而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個「虛空爆炸事件」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來有這個名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:48.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最開始只是垃圾桶裏面的空罐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:51.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近  常常發現玩偶及小孩子的包包等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易讓人放鬆警惕的物品中被放入了鋁金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還做得真過分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:59.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不一定是因為這原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:02.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但白井同學的確很擔心御阪學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:03.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是您的巨人水果冰淇淋杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:11.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:14.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初～春～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白白…白井同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:22.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在這裏偷懶膽子還真不小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  跟我去巡邏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:27.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  凍糕還…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:29.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凍糕還…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我讓初春陪我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:35.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意見就跟我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是風紀委員的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是普通人別隨便插嘴的意思麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忘記了嗎姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:50.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員的工作沒姐姐想像的那樣輕鬆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:50.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:53.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…凍糕…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  那麼囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上老是掛著風紀委員風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Judgment  Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:01.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼至少在我把不良少年幹掉之前趕來一次看看啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:11.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  這樣也好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會再還給她就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:15.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那麼悠閒地在這偷什麼懶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧  被派來增援的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:29.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  那個…你說這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實剛才把這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快點把臂章帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:33.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著  走  走去哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是工作啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:46.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你到底怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  是沒見過的臉孔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是新人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我是從今天開始配屬到此的御阪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:08:01.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪…御阪…好像在哪聽說過的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  請問前輩名叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:06.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是177支部的固法美偉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教！  固法前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:14.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓她見識一下我也是能夠勝任風紀委員的工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:14.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(431,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:18.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼槍林箭雨儘管給我打過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:19.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:23.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:25.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是掃把啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們收到了打掃這裏的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:35.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…那個  我是風紀委員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:35.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(383,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:40.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊  學生們亂丟的垃圾由我們風紀委員來收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:40.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(433,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實習的時候沒學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  說起來的確是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員的工作就是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(230,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著  給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:03.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這個也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了  給我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:14.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我的厲…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:25.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  居然忘記帶臂章  不謹慎也得有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:34.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是沒看到類似的東西  也沒寄放在櫃檯上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:35.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢討書先別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時回到支部取備用的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:51.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行  像那樣隨便使用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:01.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:03.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼「但是」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保衛治安和風紀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和行使武力是兩碼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:09.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是  的確在實習當中…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我在實習的內容之前  先以普通的常識來考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員的工作可沒有那麼輕鬆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:25.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會認真做好工作給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:32.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…嗯  那加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:39.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…我根本不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:51.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然實習和現場工作有很大差別嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  真沒有想到  自己會連看地圖都一竅不通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:57.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有輕重  甚至連察言觀色都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原來也不擅長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於地圖的查看方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是熟悉的街道  也意外的費工夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  我是固法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:21.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我們也會幫忙尋找的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:24.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到尋找失物的請求了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:25.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找失物？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  好像是個包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:33.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近  常常發現玩偶及小孩子的包包等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:36.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易讓人放鬆警惕的物品中被放入了鋁金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:39.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莫非是小孩子用的包包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這都被你知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是粉紅色的  上面還有花朵的圖案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:48.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是放在長椅上的時候被狗叼走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被…被狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:54.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那可不得了  得趕緊把那隻狗抓住才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  要是途中被丟棄的話就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:58.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟棄…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會被誰撿走帶回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十萬火急  得趕緊把包找回來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:09.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:17.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  我沒辦法穿過這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:21.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我也是勉勉強強才能挪動…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:24.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪同學  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏好像有一條腿很多的蟲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  到底跑到哪裏去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:38.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏好像有一條沒有腿的蟲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:44.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:53.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  又不是在找貓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼想都找錯地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:58.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪同學  再往右一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:06.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…這樣亂動的話…我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:11.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  D地區也沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:15.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  感謝你們的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了  初春在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:26.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  這裏是風紀委員第177支部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:26.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:28.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:31.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首讓我好找的歌  總算被我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經累得睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春已經有孩子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:40.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:42.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  她什麼時候才會長出花來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:44.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又不是長出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說那裏麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:49.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了  我才沒有生寶寶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:50.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你瞧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看的話  你倆的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  再不安靜點就要把她吵醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪佐天同學亂說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:00.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:03.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:07.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  她是來委託我們幫她找包的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:12.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是父母送給她的生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:15.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在委託其他支部幫忙尋找期間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:18.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我和白井同學負責照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  居然需要向其他支部求援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得有些小題大做麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:28.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園都市的人不是基本都和家人分開了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:32.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這種事  大家都會倍顯積極哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:37.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員的工作還真不簡單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:37.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(230,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:44.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底跑哪裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:57.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞了人後連一句道歉的話也不會說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你隨便開口了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:07.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:09.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:09.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:15.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏沒事了  你們兩個人合起來幹這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:16.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:17.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:18.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:23.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍…忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:26.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:29.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不會早點來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:36.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:38.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:39.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在這裏麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說還沒有找過的地方的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:50.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這裏很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:54.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在這裏的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:57.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  也可能會有怕狗的小孩子在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:00.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是怕不怕狗的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  萬一被咬的話可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  事情沒那麼簡單吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們開始找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:07.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪同學就負責那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:10.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐是風紀委員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:20.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是常盤台中學的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:26.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙子下面居然穿著短褲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要穿這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是身為大小姐的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:32.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有普通的內褲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿在短褲裏面了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:35.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒穿內褲～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒穿內褲的風紀委員～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固法前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:47.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:49.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:51.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:52.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:58.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:02.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:03.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別把我看扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:09.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥  不愧是常盤台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:19.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大功告成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:21.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣粗率地拿著不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聯絡爆破物處理組的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆破物？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:38.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  可別再弄丟了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:39.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:41.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:44.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是固法前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:46.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到它的並不是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你們認識御阪同學麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:55.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼認不認識的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:58.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是御阪美琴啊  就是常盤台中學的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:01.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪…美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:04.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個「超電磁炮」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:04.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  為什麼御阪學姐會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:09.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濕成那副樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:14.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為  她為了保護包而奮不顧身地跳進了噴水池
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:18.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是誤將包認作是炸彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:24.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明明都跟姐姐大人說到那個份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  或許這才符合御阪學姐的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:35.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑…黑子  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要那麼慌張哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盤台的超電磁炮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  露餡了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:55.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:20:00.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:06.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:11.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:12.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:17.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可真夠嗆的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是您自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:23.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一賭氣就跑去假裝風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:23.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:25.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您到底要孩子氣到什麼程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:27.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必好好反省一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員的工作可真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(230,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:34.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是真的對黑子刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:40.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不枉我苦等至今
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請對我刮目相看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的每一寸肌膚都盡收眼底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜  此刮目非彼刮目啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:52.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:56.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  來吧  來吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:41.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:41.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:44.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立即從這裏撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:46.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請問  我的店裏出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.29,0:22:49.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們觀測到重力子的活動加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:50.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家店有被安置了炸彈的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:55.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸…炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.66,0:22:58.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  到底在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.01,0:23:00.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:03.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我的腳扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:04.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡快避難
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:05.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:08.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:19.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:21.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:26.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了保護我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:32.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做  我要做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:34.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說做就做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:36.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就做給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:37.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做啥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:39.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你是哪位

